OL,5, More people - mostly women - have been 
OL,6, underpaid their state pension than     
OL,7, previously thought, latest government  
OL,8, figures show.                          
OL,10,FA new estimate suggests 237,000 state  
OL,11,Fpensioners were paid less than their   
OL,12,Fentitlement, with a total of nearly    
OL,13,F#1.5bn underpaid.                      
OL,15,FThat is 105,000 more people affected   
OL,16,Fthan the Department for Work and       
OL,17,FPensions (DWP) calculated a year ago.  
OL,19,FThey include widows and divorcees who  
OL,20,Fcould have been underpaid for years.   
